Marie-Françoise Audollent https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie-Fran%C3%A7oise_Audollent 0 Marie-Françoise Audollent (22 May 1943 – 30 March 2008) was a French actress. She was known for her role in The Da Vinci Code. Her other roles have included Éloge de l'amour and Le Comte de Monte Cristo.
